these manifests are applied using kubectl before chart installation
see https://github.com/helm/charts/issues/9941#issuecomment-447844259

```
curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/coreos/prometheus-operator/master/example/prometheus-operator-crd/alertmanager.crd.yaml >  ./alertmanager.crd.yaml && \
curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/coreos/prometheus-operator/master/example/prometheus-operator-crd/prometheus.crd.yaml >  ./prometheus.crd.yaml && \
curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/coreos/prometheus-operator/master/example/prometheus-operator-crd/prometheusrule.crd.yaml >  ./prometheusrule.crd.yaml && \
curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/coreos/prometheus-operator/master/example/prometheus-operator-crd/servicemonitor.crd.yaml >  ./servicemonitor.crd.yaml
```
